</section>

<section class="section">
  <h3>Goals</h3>
  <p>
    The eLearning platform is designed to:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Provide flexible, on-demand training to support both new and tenured employees.</li>
    <li>Support consistent process understanding across functional domains.</li>
